maintext:
ROCKY HILL, Conn. (AP) _ The winning numbers in Saturday afternoon’s drawing of the Connecticut Lottery’s “Lucky Links Day” game were:
01-05-07-08-11-15-20-22
(one, five, seven, eight, eleven, fifteen, twenty, twenty-two)
